<p class="lead">Start doing. Commit to a step, and live it out this week.</p>

<ul>
  <li>What’s your next step for living out your new label? How can you start this week?</li>
  <li>This week, memorize <a href="https://www.bible.com/bible/116/2co.5.17.nlt">2 Corinthians 5:17</a></li>
